ch/component/k2/1537067-20200710.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537067-20200710.htm&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=8affefb6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537067-20200710.htm&h=5dde4d35\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537067-20200710.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁撚驚做乜"},{"pid":"7b804a16e64548b43a68cd20729b4b94a858caff","tid":2102511,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"ID 4個位<br />\n生日<br />\n唔見得trace到我出黎"},{"pid":"dbf54e78483595b315468bf9cce781c6914468e8","tid":2102511,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"乜你張票有名架咩?"},{"pid":"ad1ea49ef81f3623c1af9652a660789a54b4f359","tid":2102511,"uid":34093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:48:45.000Z","msg":"都係果句啦, 要拉你你上連登都已經拉左你啦,<br />\n應該改改標題: 使用互聯網連接海外恐違國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d63e1f58cc0fb4fb6d30fb63d5b4984a5bebd9","tid":2102511,"uid":134206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"上連登開post都好危險嫁"},{"pid":"78709990fed29e7db0656a558a1814f3e6bde4bd","tid":2102511,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:49:53.000Z","msg":"聽日係睇住址証明，又唔係抄你資料<br />\n比佢睇完就投得票，怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過點都會去投<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8faced93a67802e1a38d90a8c7daf5178401301","tid":2102511,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:50: